      <RecitationInstruction>
         <ab>Vid. Nērangs.</ab>
         <ab><em>aṣ̌əm vohū</em>] <em>aṣ̌əm vohī</em> III gwptn' plʾhwm PWN III bʾl hwltn' cygwn PWN yšt YHWWN-yt OD <em>vispaiiā̊ druuatō stōiš</em> (VrS11.22) 2065.</ab>
      </RecitationInstruction>
