   <Parallels/>
   <Ritual>
      <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
         <ab>VrS11.16 Var a (mss. 2007, 2010, 2030, 2040, 2065, 2070, 2109, 4000, 4010, 4020, 4025, 4040, 4161, 4162, 5020, 4030a):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            <em>aṣ̌əm vohū</em> sē xwandār guftan parāhōm pad sē bār xwardan  harw bār-ē rāspīg <em>aṣ̌əm vohū</em> dō guftan ud bōy ō ī ātaxš dādan ud zōt dahān pāk kardan ud 
            dast harw dō pad pādyāb kardan ud dast ī hōy abar barsom dast nihādan</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "The reciter should  recite three times the <em>aṣ̌əm vohū</em> and drink the <em>parāhōm</em> in three times. Each time, the <em>rāspīg</em> should recite two <em>aṣ̌əm vohū</em> 
            and the <em>zōt</em> should clean his mouth, wash his two hands with <em>pādyāb</em> and put his left hand on the <em>barsom</em>."</ab>
      </Nerangs>
   </Ritual>
